Stock

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • Stock.Item

  • public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents any item and its given properties, possessing at least: (Name, Manufacturing Costs, Sell Price, Reorder Point, Reorder Amount, Temperature) Note that not all items are temperature controlled, and so they will not need a temperature.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Kwun Hyo Lee & Jonathan Wai
